		"Name": "Hunchback",
		"Details": "The Hunchback's a certified classic on the battlefield. More Hunchback variants exist than almost any other BattleMech ever made and this, the HBK-4O, is just one more for the pile. Built by the pirates of the Oberon Confederation the HBK-4O is primarily armed with a quartet of the Confederation's new Pepperbox Rifles for unexpected burst damage. However, after the Pepperboxes run dry, all that the -4O can contribute is a Large Laser, plus the Hunchback's famously powerful fist weapons. For power the -4O relies on a 200-rated standard fusion engine while Light Plating Armor provides free tonnage for the weapons and Pirate-Accelerated Myomer provides surprising bursts of speed in combat.",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_hunchback"
